data.title: Find Your Neighborhood
data.text:
The City of Fargo is committed to supporting neighborhood integrity because strong neighborhoods make for a strong communityâ€”they are the basic building blocks of a city.

For more information on your neighborhood, first hover your mouse over your neighborhood on the interactive map, to highlight. Then, click to bring up the window with the link to more details. Alternatively, if you know which neighborhood you live in, view the current list of neighborhoods.

To find more information on community demographics visit the American FactFinder website.
